fono (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Single-binary local STT + LLM (whisper.cpp + llama.cpp coexist).
  * Default hotkeys: F9 (toggle), F8 (push-to-talk).
  * Wizard offers local LLM cleanup with tier-aware Qwen2.5 model picker.
  * Tray STT/LLM submenus mark the active backend; auto-download with
    notifications when switching to local.
  * Hardware-acceleration banner; LLM startup logging trimmed.

